[30;1m15 | [0m[35m  * This allows the caller to provide a password for a gMSA or machine account that could contain in[0m
[30;1m16 | [0m[35m* Stop using deprecated `datetime.dateime.utcnow()` for CredSSP acceptor context[0m
[30;1m17 | [0m[35m* Treat an empty string as a valid password, `None` is kept as use the cached credential[0m
[30;1m18 | [0m[35m* Improve the exception shown when no password was provided and no cached credential was available[0m
